  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "> Bioinformatics is an interdisciplinary field that develops methods and software tools for understanding biological data. — [Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bioinformatics)",
    "context": "> Bioinformatics is an interdisciplinary field that develops methods and software tools for understanding biological data. — [Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bioinformatics)\n\nA curated list of awesome Bioinformatics software, resources, and libraries. Mostly command line based, and free or open-source. Please feel free to [contribute](CONTRIBUTING.md)!\n\n<!-- START doctoc generated TOC please keep comment here to allow auto update -->\n<!-- DON'T EDIT THIS SECTION, INSTEAD RE-RUN doctoc TO UPDATE -->",
